e":"2020-02-24T06:01:57.000Z","msg":"推，幫手！"},{"pid":"6facc9f86b0ac5fef82601fe2e5707c0712bd111","tid":1894608,"uid":110699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T06:04:24.000Z","msg":"咁點搵佢"},{"pid":"4f6af1369037a63bd573f0d43c1e9e7b885b743a","tid":1894608,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T06:05:39.000Z","msg":"唔好怕羞眾籌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾個月前都有個大學手足眾籌學費"},{"pid":"cb236b4361ef7d6382e1555128fc034249f5ce4a","tid":1894608,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T06:05:50.000Z","msg":"學費/生活費借non-mean. 咁低息一定要借盡.<br />\n畢業後 再分開15年慢慢還"},{"pid":"bb294fec2f4b7ba2f66013d9a9837250774f5312","tid":1894608,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T06:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8oe9Do.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8oe9Do.jpg&h=b1641cf0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc514840d1e377c15ff19c660016acdd534508ad","tid":1894608,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T06:06:58.000Z","msg":"推呀屌，有無眾籌"},{"pid":"6f1ebf4b2f0f0be61f1c9d2b0112d85f277afa34","tid":1894608,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T06:07:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7501167c265bf1de0ac087f034cd57883e6efdca","tid":1894608,"uid":159870,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T06:07:05.000Z","msg":"無錢仲出街食譚仔唔自己煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}